{"id": "lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_NDc5Mw_0009", "text": "誰又有說過 愛敵人真有用", "structure": {"line_index": 9, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 5, 4, 4, 4, 2, 0, 3, 5, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["seoi4", "jau6", "jau5", "syut3", "gwo3", "oi3", "dik6", "jan4", "zan1", "jau5", "jung6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "誰", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "又", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "說", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "過", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "敵人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "真", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有用", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "零號", "artists": ["楊千嬅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_4793", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_NDc5Mw_0008", "next_line_id": "lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_NDc5Mw_0010", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_NDc5Mw_0010", "text": "如若犧牲得永生 爲何仍是愛得隱隱作痛", "structure": {"line_index": 10, "char_count": 17}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 3, 3, 3, 5, 3, 0, 0, 2, 4, 3, 9, 9, 4, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jyu4", "joek6", "hei1", "saang1", "dak1", "wing5", "sang1", "ho4", "jing4", "si6", "oi3", "dak1", "jan2", "jan2", "zok3", "tung3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "如若", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "犧牲", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "得", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "永生", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "爲何", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "仍", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "得", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "隱隱作痛", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "零號", "artists": ["楊千嬅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_4793", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_NDc5Mw_0009", "next_line_id": "lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_NDc5Mw_0011", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_NDc5Mw_0011", "text": "不必福音 別這樣 逼迫我", "structure": {"line_index": 11, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 3, 3, 3, 2, 5, 2, 3, 3, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["bat1", "bit1", "fuk1", "jam1", "bit6", "ze5", "joeng6", "bik1", "baak1", "ngo5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "不必", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "福音", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "別", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這樣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "逼迫", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "零號", "artists": ["楊千嬅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_4793", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_NDc5Mw_0010", "next_line_id": "lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_NDc5Mw_0012", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_NDc5Mw_0012", "text": "不必福音 無論誰 都不過 只得一生", "structure": {"line_index": 12, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 3, 3, 3, 0, 2, 0, 3, 3, 4, 9, 3, 3, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["bat1", "bit1", "fuk1", "jam1", "mou4", "leon6", "seoi4", "dou1", "bat1", "gwo3", "zi2", "dak1", "jat1", "sang1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "不必", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "福音", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "無論誰", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "都", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不過", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "只得", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一生", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "零號", "artists": ["楊千嬅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_4793", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_NDc5Mw_0011", "next_line_id": "lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_NDc5Mw_0013", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_NDc5Mw_0013", "text": "我不依 怎麼樣 天國已有多近", "structure": {"line_index": 13, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 3, 3, 9, 3, 2, 3, 4, 5, 5, 3, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "bat1", "ji1", "zam2", "mo1", "joeng6", "tin1", "gwok3", "ji5", "jau5", "do1", "gan6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不依", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怎麼樣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "天國", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "已有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "多近", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "零號", "artists": ["楊千嬅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_4793", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_NDc5Mw_0012", "next_line_id": "lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_NDc5Mw_0014", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
